				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The ghast do spawn one to three at a time during the night time in Lesser Faydark. <BR>
When you get 4 ghast hearts, turn them in at the Paladin guild in Felwith. He will <BR>
then continue the quest telling you to kill the necro. He spawns at night at the skele<BR>
tower in Lesser Fay. His place holder is the skele on the bottom step. You need to <BR>
time it right to get him to spawn. I found that if you kill him shortly after 2pm, and <BR>
keep the rest of the area free of yard trash, he will usually spawn. Then you must<BR>
kill the Dark Elf courier. Take the loots of both of these mobs back to the Paladin's <BR>
guild and recieve the disciple of tunare neclace. This much I have completed...getting<BR>
ready to do the third part of the quest. Hope this helps!<BR>
<BR>

